  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink64-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">talaimakaṉ parattaiyarōṭu puṉalāṭiṉāṉ eṉpatu aṟinta talaimakaḷ avaṉ maṟaittuḻic colliyatu.
        </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="Aink64">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l>alamara lāyamō ṭamartuṇai taḻīi</l>
          <l>nalamiku putuppuṉa lāṭak kaṇṭō</l>
          <l>roruvaru miruvaru mallar</l>
          <l>palarē teyyavem maṟaiyā tīmē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">


          <l> While you bathed in the delightful fresh flood, </l>
          <l rend="indent2"> embracing your friend who fits [you],</l>
          <l rend="indent4"> along with [her] girlfriends whirling [around her] – </l>
          <l> the witnesses were not just one or two people</l>
          <l> but many! </l>
          <l> Do not hide [it] from us!</l>

        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
